trans-unit.source: Specifies the security settings for the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.WSDualHttpBinding"></xref>.
This class specifies the security settings for the `wsDualHttpBinding` binding.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen angir sikkerhetsinnstillingene for den `wsDualHttpBinding` binding.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.WSDualHttpSecurity"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.WSDualHttpSecurity"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets the message-level security properties for the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.WSDualHttpBinding"></xref>.
The object returned specifies detailed message-level security properties for the `wsDualHttpBinding` binding.
trans-unit.target: Objektet som ble returnert angir detaljert melding sikkerhetsegenskaper for det `wsDualHttpBinding` binding.

trans-unit.source: The default values include: <xref:System.ServiceModel.MessageSecurityOverHttp.ClientCredentialType*> is <xref:System.ServiceModel.MessageCredentialType>, <xref:System.ServiceModel.MessageSecurityOverHttp.AlgorithmSuite*> is <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.SecurityAlgorithmSuite.Basic256*>, and <xref:System.ServiceModel.MessageSecurityOverHttp.NegotiateServiceCredential*> is <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the security mode for the parent <xref href="System.ServiceModel.WSDualHttpBinding"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir sikkerhetsmodus for overordnet <xref href="System.ServiceModel.WSDualHttpBinding"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The value of this property determines whether message-level security is applied to the binding.
trans-unit.target: Verdien for denne egenskapen bestemmer om sikkerhet på radnivå meldingen skal brukes på bindingen.

trans-unit.source: The value is not a valid <xref href="System.ServiceModel.WSDualHttpSecurityMode"></xref>.
